---
description: User-facing text must be in Spanish
alwaysApply: true
---

# UI copy in Spanish

- **All text that the user sees** (labels, buttons, placeholders, messages, page titles, descriptions, metadata title/description) must be written in **Spanish**.
- **Code** (routes, file names, variable names, component names, comments) stays in **English**.
- Keep tone neutral and clear; use standard Spanish (e.g. "Iniciar sesión", "Correo electrónico", "Contraseña", "Crear cuenta").
